| Category                       | Example                                                     | Where it belongs                                                                    |
| ------------------------------ | ----------------------------------------------------------- | ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| Shared across all environments | `INSTALLED_APPS`, `MIDDLEWARE`, `REST_FRAMEWORK`            | `base.py`                                                                           |
| Different between environments | `DEBUG`, `ALLOWED_HOSTS`, `DATABASES`, allowed CORS origins | `development.py` / `production.py`                                                  |
| Secret or deployment-specific  | `SECRET_KEY`, database passwords, API keys                  | Environment variables (`.env` in development, deployment environment in production) |
